result.name: Muscle Man

reviews.text: Famous for it's noodles, friendly staff and body-builder owners.

A very interesting place. The concept of bodybuilding and noodles does not come to mind but it works so well here. I came here because Anthony Bourdain went to it and featured it on his show “No Reservations,” but there weren’t any muscle men there when I went, unfortunately. I got the wonton noodles at the top of the menu and they tasted good. Simple but they know what they’re doing there with it. Lots of interesting picture on the walls to look at.
One of my favorite Chinese noodles restaurant
Nice little restaurant with very tasty wonton,  worth to try.
Very traditional dumpling with nice soup, noodle is also very good of quality.

reviews.text: 價錢貴了一點。食物是不錯的。但性價比返不到以前舊舖了
好難食 鼓油撈面 咁就埋單50蚊 面身又乾 水餃好hea 野飲加廿蚊 貴到痴線 呃遊客
試咗猪手捞，朋友就水餃捞，麵底煙靱彈牙，猪手軟淋啱啱好，水餃香芹味濃，有口感！絕對值得一試。
呢度牛筋超正，一定要試下
炸豬大腸有些失望，價錢略貴了些！
